6️⃣ Check cluster storage capacity (important)
If using Red Hat OpenShift Data Foundation, check storage capacity:
oc get cephcluster -n openshift-storage
Or check:
oc get storagecluster -n openshift-storage
Because available storage pool capacity also matters, not just maximum volume size.
